310
00:23:22,300 --> 00:23:23,140
Hong.

311
00:23:23,420 --> 00:23:24,820
I miss you so much!

312
00:23:25,460 --> 00:23:26,100
How about

313
00:23:26,660 --> 00:23:27,900
I never saw you and

314
00:23:28,060 --> 00:23:29,620
you never saw me?

315
00:23:29,780 --> 00:23:30,540
I'll go out.

316
00:23:30,580 --> 00:23:30,940
Stop.

317
00:23:30,940 --> 00:23:31,380
Stay.

318
00:23:32,300 --> 00:23:33,740
If you still want to live,

319
00:23:34,340 --> 00:23:35,420
just do as I tell you,

320
00:23:36,020 --> 00:23:36,740
or...

321
00:23:38,580 --> 00:23:40,140
Okay.

322
00:23:40,460 --> 00:23:41,380
Stop messing with me.

323
00:23:41,540 --> 00:23:42,380
I can't help you guys.

324
00:23:42,780 --> 00:23:43,460
Hong.

325
00:23:43,820 --> 00:23:44,540
Let me ask you,

326
00:23:45,060 --> 00:23:47,260
