328
00:23:48,180 --> 00:23:48,820
No.

329
00:23:48,980 --> 00:23:49,740
Who has it then?

330
00:23:50,660 --> 00:23:52,340
There's a stupid fat guy.

331
00:23:52,420 --> 00:23:53,100
He has it.

332
00:23:54,100 --> 00:23:55,220
