340
00:24:08,580 --> 00:24:09,940
Bai Haotian? I don't know where she is.

341
00:24:11,460 --> 00:24:12,020
Umm,

342
00:24:12,260 --> 00:24:13,380
I can get the key for you.

343
00:24:13,580 --> 00:24:14,740
