348
00:24:22,540 --> 00:24:24,340
We've been friends for years, right?

349
00:24:24,380 --> 00:24:25,180
Let's help him.

350
00:24:25,900 --> 00:24:26,940
Let's drink together and

351
00:24:27,140 --> 00:24:28,100
escape together.

352
00:24:28,300 --> 00:24:28,780
No problem.

353
00:24:29,460 --> 00:24:30,420
