371
00:25:07,300 --> 00:25:07,820
Almost there.

372
00:25:07,900 --> 00:25:08,380
Almost…

373
00:25:08,460 --> 00:25:08,980
Enough.

374
00:25:10,620 --> 00:25:11,180
You are not drinking?

375
00:25:11,740 --> 00:25:12,460
You are not drinking?

376
00:25:13,460 --> 00:25:14,220
I'll pour you some more.

377
00:25:17,380 --> 00:25:18,380
Are you alright?

378
00:25:18,420 --> 00:25:19,380
Is he alright?

379
00:25:19,580 --> 00:25:20,740
