389
00:25:52,300 --> 00:25:53,260
Don't try to ditch me.

390
00:25:55,180 --> 00:25:55,740
Of course not!

391
00:25:55,940 --> 00:25:57,820
We can't let Hong break our old friendship.

392
00:25:57,900 --> 00:25:59,420
We won't lie to people.

393
00:25:59,620 --> 00:26:00,500
Surely not, Hong.

394
00:26:04,460 --> 00:26:04,940
Let's go.

395
00:26:05,340 --> 00:26:06,580
But you are not "people".

396
00:26:07,260 --> 00:26:07,740
I…

397
00:26:10,300 --> 00:26:11,460
Why do you still not understand

398
00:26:11,540 --> 00:26:13,220
after so many times?

399
00:26:14,020 --> 00:26:15,460
We won't let you leave with us

400
00:26:15,700 --> 00:26:16,980
because we want to save your life.

401
00:26:19,100 --> 00:26:19,700
Kylin.

402
00:26:20,580 --> 00:26:21,900
You go save Glasses.

403
00:26:22,180 --> 00:26:22,740
Fatty

404
00:26:22,940 --> 00:26:24,380
and I will get Liu Sang and Bai Haotian out.

405
00:26:27,060 --> 00:26:28,060
Baby.

406
00:26:28,700 --> 00:26:30,020
I have wanted to sleep with you for a long time.

407
00:26:30,100 --> 00:26:31,100
Go away!

408
00:26:31,340 --> 00:26:32,340
Go away!

409
00:26:32,500 --> 00:26:33,380
Go away!

410
00:26:33,660 --> 00:26:34,060
Pooh!

411
00:26:34,100 --> 00:26:34,500
I…

412
00:26:36,140 --> 00:26:36,980
Do you want to die?

413
00:26:41,700 --> 00:26:43,340
Didn't Jiang Ziyan tell you

414
00:26:43,740 --> 00:26:45,300
Wu Xie's women

415
00:26:45,500 --> 00:26:47,460
