421
00:27:03,660 --> 00:27:04,620
No!

422
00:27:24,780 --> 00:27:25,620
Don't move.

423
00:27:26,700 --> 00:27:27,660
Wait for Kylin's signal.

424
00:27:29,180 --> 00:27:30,620
After we get Liu Sang,

425
00:27:31,220 --> 00:27:32,820
