426
00:27:33,180 --> 00:27:33,580
Okay.

427
00:27:33,580 --> 00:27:34,420
I'll save Bai Haotian.

428
00:27:52,060 --> 00:27:52,860
Kylin is on the move!

429
00:27:53,020 --> 00:27:53,460
Go!

430
00:27:56,340 --> 00:27:56,740
Liu Sang.

431
00:27:58,900 --> 00:27:59,260
Are you alright?

432
00:27:59,420 --> 00:27:59,820
Sang.

433
00:28:00,180 --> 00:28:00,740
Where's Bai Haotian?

434
00:28:01,860 --> 00:28:03,060
She's in danger! Hurry up!

435
00:28:03,300 --> 00:28:04,180
Go away!

436
00:28:04,900 --> 00:28:05,540
Go away!

437
00:28:06,140 --> 00:28:07,140
Help.

438
00:28:07,460 --> 00:28:08,660
Help!

439
00:29:05,380 --> 00:29:05,940
Let's go.

440
00:29:15,380 --> 00:29:15,980
Someone broke in.

441
00:29:35,940 --> 00:29:36,900
What's going on?

442
00:29:37,700 --> 00:29:40,300
Wu Xie took Bai Haotian with him.

443
00:29:48,180 --> 00:29:48,860
Get them back!

444
00:29:52,620 --> 00:29:53,300
Where is Wu Xie?

445
00:29:53,460 --> 00:29:54,980
Wu Xie went to rescue Bai.

446
00:29:55,100 --> 00:29:56,260
You guys wait here.

447
00:29:56,420 --> 00:29:57,380
I have to find them.

448
00:29:59,220 --> 00:30:00,020
Go.

449
00:30:20,900 --> 00:30:21,660
Naive.

450
00:31:12,660 --> 00:31:13,620
Hurry!

451
00:31:35,380 --> 00:31:36,180
Freeze!

452
00:31:46,620 --> 00:31:47,740
Is everyone okay?

453
00:31:52,460 --> 00:31:53,980
I knew you would come to save me.

454
00:31:54,100 --> 00:31:55,260
Actually, Chief saved you.

455
00:31:55,420 --> 00:31:56,820
This is not the time to argue about this!

456
00:31:56,980 --> 00:31:58,700
I am here. You guys will be fine!

457
00:31:58,900 --> 00:32:00,780
Old soldiers never die.

458
00:32:06,340 --> 00:32:06,740
What happened?

459
00:32:06,740 --> 00:32:07,500
Whose blood is this?

460
00:32:11,780 --> 00:32:12,060
Fatty!

461
00:32:12,220 --> 00:32:12,580
Fatty!

462
00:32:12,700 --> 00:32:13,340
Come on.

463
00:32:13,420 --> 00:32:14,420
Get him here.

464
00:32:14,580 --> 00:32:15,300
Sit here.

465
00:32:16,980 --> 00:32:17,500
What happened?

466
00:32:17,620 --> 00:32:18,220
What's going on?

467
00:32:19,020 --> 00:32:19,860
You got shot.

468
00:32:20,140 --> 00:32:21,500
I won' t make it.

469
00:32:22,540 --> 00:32:23,420
Naive.

470
00:32:23,820 --> 00:32:25,020
I didn't expect that

471
00:32:25,620 --> 00:32:27,860
I'll die before you.

472
00:32:28,580 --> 00:32:30,380
I'll be waiting for you

473
00:32:30,540 --> 00:32:33,180
-in another world.
-Stop talking.

474
00:32:50,500 --> 00:32:51,820
Kylin.

475
00:32:52,020 --> 00:32:54,180
You are the one I worry about the most.

476
00:32:54,340 --> 00:32:55,620
After the two of us die,

477
00:32:55,780 --> 00:32:58,100
you'll be left alone.

478
00:32:58,500 --> 00:32:59,900
But no matter

479
00:33:00,660 --> 00:33:01,980
