00:33:09,100 --> 00:33:09,820
It's just a scratch.

483
00:33:12,340 --> 00:33:13,300
Stop talking nonsense.

484
00:33:13,460 --> 00:33:14,180
Take it.

485
00:33:14,380 --> 00:33:15,620
Hold the gauze and press your wound.

486
00:33:18,100 --> 00:33:19,220
According to the instructions of Uncle Sanxing,

487
00:33:19,980 --> 00:33:21,860
