488
00:33:22,020 --> 00:33:23,940
to find the entrance of Thunder City.

489
00:33:24,260 --> 00:33:25,500
Let's go.

490
00:33:53,340 --> 00:33:54,340
Hold me up.

491
00:33:54,860 --> 00:33:56,260
I thought you're not hurt seriously.

492
00:33:56,380 --> 00:33:58,140
My hand is hurt.

493
00:34:00,700 --> 00:34:01,380
Kylin.

494
00:34:01,740 --> 00:34:02,860
Kylin, here.

495
00:34:07,060 --> 00:34:07,980
Are you okay?

496
00:34:08,900 --> 00:34:09,340
I am fine.

497
00:34:19,660 --> 00:34:20,300
Come on.

498
00:34:22,820 --> 00:34:24,220
Hurry up, Glasses!

499
00:34:28,420 --> 00:34:29,490
