500
00:34:50,490 --> 00:34:51,300
There is a door here.

501
00:35:00,450 --> 00:35:01,660
Come on!

502
00:35:04,300 --> 00:35:04,930
Fatty.

503
00:35:09,260 --> 00:35:10,780
These pagodas are all connected to each other.

504
00:35:20,020 --> 00:35:21,580
Someone is coming.

505
00:35:21,740 --> 00:35:22,580
Let's go!

506
00:35:23,500 --> 00:35:24,820
This way.

507
00:35:48,500 --> 00:35:49,420
It's a dead end.

508
00:35:50,380 --> 00:35:51,220
We hit a dead end.

509
00:35:54,340 --> 00:35:55,420
