512
00:36:03,980 --> 00:36:05,540
The scene painted on the mural we saw earlier.

513
00:36:05,860 --> 00:36:07,020
I'll go down and have a look first.

514
00:36:11,580 --> 00:36:12,380
Someone is coming.

515
00:36:15,900 --> 00:36:16,940
Be careful.

516
00:37:11,140 --> 00:37:11,980
Bai.

517
00:37:12,180 --> 00:37:12,940
Naive!

518
00:37:16,260 --> 00:37:16,940
Bai!

519
00:37:17,780 --> 00:37:18,300
Bai!

520
00:37:18,460 --> 00:37:19,180
Bai!

521
00:37:19,340 --> 00:37:20,220
Where's the mechanism?

522
00:37:20,740 --> 00:37:21,940
Where is the switch?

523
00:37:39,580 --> 00:37:40,740
Bai!

524
00:37:40,900 --> 00:37:41,500
Bai!

525
00:37:41,660 --> 00:37:42,780
Hide. Come on!

526
00:38:07,220 --> 00:38:09,300
It is impolite not to reciprocate.

527
00:38:10,460 --> 00:38:13,100
Let me give you a big gift!

528
00:38:24,740 --> 00:38:25,220
Come on.

529
00:38:25,700 --> 00:38:26,620
Bai.

530
00:38:26,820 --> 00:38:28,300
There is indeed a tunnel underwater.

531
00:38:28,460 --> 00:38:29,100
Hurry.

532
00:38:29,260 --> 00:38:30,180
Retreat.

533
00:38:31,340 --> 00:38:32,580
Go into the water.

534
00:38:32,740 --> 00:38:33,300
Go.

535
00:38:38,420 --> 00:38:41,180
Let me give you another big gift!

536
00:39:14,940 --> 00:39:15,980
What's inside like?

