546
00:39:47,900 --> 00:39:50,420
This place looks pretty safe.

547
00:39:54,460 --> 00:39:55,820
I like it here.

548
00:39:56,020 --> 00:39:57,620
I don't know where we are.

549
00:39:57,860 --> 00:39:59,580
But anyway, there is meat, so we won't starve.

550
00:40:00,500 --> 00:40:01,380
Fatty.

551
00:40:01,940 --> 00:40:03,420
Do you remember that mural?

552
00:40:04,260 --> 00:40:06,460
I think we got

553
00:40:06,660 --> 00:40:07,900
to the other side of the mountain from the waterway painted in the mural.

554
00:40:08,660 --> 00:40:09,420
This is probably...

555
00:40:09,580 --> 00:40:10,380
Thunder City.

556
00:40:13,180 --> 00:40:13,860
Yes.

557
00:40:14,100 --> 00:40:15,340
This place is Thunder City.

558
00:40:16,300 --> 00:40:17,780
I looked around.

559
00:40:18,220 --> 00:40:21,100
The terrain here is exactly the same as the mural.

560
00:40:23,820 --> 00:40:26,260
But this place is only just the perimeter of the city.

561
00:40:27,380 --> 00:40:28,460
As for the main city,

562
00:40:29,020 --> 00:40:30,860
